data.comment: The first-half is now underway.
Max Svensson (Helsingborg) gets in a header on goal but the attempt is cleared.
In the minute 5, Kalmar awarded a free kick in their own half.
Free kick Kalmar.
Kalmar drive upfield and Romarinho gets in a shot. The strike is blocked by a Helsingborg defender.
In the minute 8, Free kick for Helsingborg in their own half.
Throw-in Kalmar.
Throw-in for Kalmar in their own half.
In the minute 10, Throw-in for Helsingborg at Olympia.
Andreas Ekberg signals a free kick to Kalmar in their own half.
Max Svensson puts the ball in the net and the home team now lead 1-0.
In the minute 16, Ball goes out of play for a Helsingborg goal kick.
Free kick for Helsingborg in their own half.
Joseph Ceesay (Helsingborg) gets a yellow card.
In the minute 22, Can Helsingborg get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Kalmar's half?
Fidan Aliti (Kalmar) is first to the ball but his header is off-target.
Helsingborg have a goal kick.
In the minute 25, Andreas Ekberg awards the away team a throw-in.
Andreas Ekberg signals a free kick to Kalmar in their own half.
Kalmar awarded a free kick in their own half.
In the minute 31, Andreas Ekberg awards Helsingborg a goal kick.
Throw-in high up the field for Kalmar in Helsingborg.
Kalmar awarded a throw-in in their own half.
In the minute 38, Andreas Ekberg signals a free kick to Helsingborg.
Helsingborg have been awarded a corner by Andreas Ekberg.
The first-half has come to a close in Helsingborg.
In the minute 46, The second-half is now underway.
A throw-in for the home team on the opposite half.
Free kick for Helsingborg in the half of Kalmar.
In the minute 50, Kalmar's York Raphael breaks free at Olympia. But the strike goes wide of the post.
Goal kick for Kalmar at Olympia.
Free kick for Helsingborg in their own half.
In the minute 58, The away team have replaced Mayron George with Edvin Crona. This is the first substitution made today by Nanne Bergstrand.
Corner awarded to Kalmar.
Kalmar to take a throw-in in Helsingborg territory.
In the minute 62, In Helsingborg a free kick has been awarded the away team.
At Olympia, Mohammed Abubakari has been yellow-carded for the home team.
Ball safe as Helsingborg is awarded a throw-in in their half.
In the minute 66, Jakob Voelkerling Persson is replacing Martin Olsson for the home team.
Nanne Bergstrand (Kalmar) is making a second substitution, with Filip Sachpekidis replacing York Raphael.
Kalmar's Edvin Crona attacks the ball with his head but his effort fails to hit the target.
In the minute 72, Edvin Crona gets an equalizer for Kalmar. The score is now 1-1.
Great play from Filip Sachpekidis to set up the goal.
Throw-in for Kalmar at Olympia.
In the minute 76, Andreas Ekberg signals a free kick to Helsingborg in their own half.
In Helsingborg Kalmar drive forward through Filip Sachpekidis. His shot is on target but it's saved.
Kalmar awarded a free kick in their own half.
In the minute 82, Jakob Voelkerling Persson is booked for the home team.
Andreas Ekberg awards the away team a throw-in.
Joseph Ceesay (Helsingborg) is given an opening but the shot is blocked by a defender.
In the minute 85, Andreas Ekberg signals a Kalmar throw-in in Helsingborg's half.
Throw-in Kalmar.
Kalmar have been awarded a corner by Andreas Ekberg.
In the minute 88, Armin Gigovic (Helsingborg) gets a yellow card. He will be suspended from the next match!
Free kick for Helsingborg in their own half.
Andreas Ekberg signals a free kick to Helsingborg in their own half.
That's full-time at Olympia. The final score is 1-1.
